About the Product:
Indulge in the exhilarating world of Korean cuisine with our Kimchi Noodles. Taste the fiery thrill of our secret Kimchi blend, delivering a spice burst of sensational gochujang flavour. Elevate your culinary experience with 2 sachets – the Saucemaker, ensuring an infused flavor while cooking, and the Sprinkler, to add an extra kick after cooking for an unforgettable feast.
Ingredients:
Noodles: Refined Wheat Flour (Maida), Refined Palm Oil, Iodized Salt, Thickener (E412), Stabilizer (E451(I)), Raising Agent (E500(Ii), Antioxidant (E319) Saucemaker: Maltodextrin, Soya Sauce Powder, Salt, Sugar, Spices And Condiments (Garlic, Onion, Chilli, Parsley, Pepper), Corn Flour, Yeast Extract Powder, Hydrolyzed Vegetable Protein (Soya), Flavor Enhancer (Ins 627, Ins 631), Anticaking Agent (Ins 551), Natural & Nature Identical Flavoring Substances, Acidity Regulator (Ins 330).
Allergen Information: Contains Soya.
Sprinkler: Sesame Seeds
Allergen Information: Contains Sesame
Nutritional Facts:
Per 100g Serving Size: 89g; No. of Servings: 1;

Energy(kcal):421.2
Protein(g): 7.1
Carbohydrate(g): 66;
Total Sugar(g):3.7;
